'''Tom''' was the son of [[Nan Smithson]] and the grandson of [[Smith Smithson]], the title character of the story ''[[Smith of Wootton Major]]''.  Smith affectionately referred to his grandson as "[[Tomling]]".<ref>[[J.R.R. Tolkien]], ''[[Smith of Wootton Major]]''</ref>

